// A standalone type emitter: stroke STKWR-T, then append any type to write it
// anywhere (assertions, casts, free-standing annotations). Base emits nothing;
// STKWR-T/TPH -> number, STKWR-T/PR/STR -> Promise<string>, STKWR-T/SKP -> free.
